#   
#   NAME
#      ProgressWindow - Creates a progress window.
#      
#   SYNOPSIS
#      ProgressWindow toplevelWindow ?options?
#      
#   SPECIFIC OPTIONS
#      -cancelcmd, cancelCmd, CancelCmd
#      -font1, font1, Font1
#      -font2, font2, Font2
#      -name, name, Name
#      -pausecmd, pauseCmd, PauseCmd
#      -percent, percent, Percent
#      -text, text, Text
#      -text2, text2, Text2
